name: Lemnis Lighting
overview: Lemnis Lighting B.V. develops and markets light emitting diodes lamps for consumer, business, business, and public service markets. It offers indoor and outdoor lighting products for hospitality, residential areas, parks rural areas, tunnels, parking spaces, cycle paths, public roads, and thoroughfares. The company also provides greenhouse lighting products that include assimilation lamps for growth acceleration; and luminaires for multi-layer cultivation. In addition, it offers solar lighting models for personal use, fixed installation, and public lighting. The company was founded in 2005 and is based in ‘s-Hertogenbosch, the Netherlands with additional offices in the Netherlands, San Francisco, Hong Kong, and Singapore. Lemnis Lighting B.V. is a subsidiary of Tendris.
